title: Independent Candidate Rana Abdul Manan wins PP-272 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 10 (APP): Independent Candidate, Rana Abdul Manan Sajid has won the Punjab Assembly election from PP-272, Muzaffargarh-V by securing 33,453 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Makhdoomzada Syed Basit Ahmed Sultan of Pakistan Muslim League-Nawaz (PML-N) who bagged 29,934 votes.
Overall votersâ€™ turn-out remained 50.91%.
